{"tw": {"2866440": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Lily’s Labyrinth of Lust", "steam_appid": 2866440, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h1>藍圖</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/2d60ecdb386f16500e2389acfb531012.avif?t=1742849812\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras_big/2d60ecdb386f16500e2389acfb531012.avif?t=1742849812 width=800 height=308 /></span></p></p><br><h1>關於此遊戲</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/bb616306487ed393f57c23480d0afd49.poster.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/bb616306487ed393f57c23480d0afd49.webm?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/bb616306487ed393f57c23480d0afd49.mp4?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/f5e10d48e98d863810aee5765bbdaa5d.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >親愛的，你在愜意的頂樓公寓裡的生活即將發生轉變。我會追捕你，監視你的一舉一動，而我的腦海裡只有一件事......支配。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lily's Labyrinth of Lust 是一場令人心跳加速的貓鼠遊戲。如果你能勝過我，或許你就能掌控一切，但如果被我逮到？好吧，這麼說吧，你會發現你到底能承受多少。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能承受我無情的注視，想辦法讓我分心，抵抗我的嘲弄，努力跟上我的步伐嗎？還是你會投降，讓我帶你經歷一場永生難忘的狂野旅程？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>- 莉莉(Lily)</i></p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/773523458ac125752f9ba40fb8458c0f.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/b1996e8b9c0722aeea68a9a39ca1d23d.poster.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/b1996e8b9c0722aeea68a9a39ca1d23d.webm?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/b1996e8b9c0722aeea68a9a39ca1d23d.mp4?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>角色/「誰是莉莉？」</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lily 是你的女朋友，但別被她的愛情騙了--她是一個被控制欲驅使的花癡。她不顧一切地追逐你，不惜一切讓你屈服。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一開始，Lily 可能看起來很俏皮、很愛挑逗，但不要被她騙了。隨著遊戲的進展，Lily 會變得更加無情，讓她變得更具侵略性，並會注意到您的一舉一動。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她俏皮的奚落語在您耳邊迴盪，讓您不敢貿然逃走，然而每一次嘗試，她都會以火熱的決心拉近距離。一旦她盯上你，你就無法逃脫她無比的飢渴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lily 不只是在追逐您，她也在玩弄您的情緒。準備好迎接她意想不到的行為轉變，不要被她的甜言蜜語所迷惑，不管她看起來有多有說服力。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/1dfdeba352b6c735eec260ff84cd4850.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=200 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/ca2123eb67efaa8bb091789d651d22d6.poster.avif?t=1742849812\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/ca2123eb67efaa8bb091789d651d22d6.webm?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/ca2123eb67efaa8bb091789d651d22d6.mp4?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊戲玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在她追捕您的過程中，您需要使用所有您能找到的物品，例如屁眼塞或您值得信賴的電擊槍，這些物品可能會暫時壓制她貪得無厭的慾望，但別被騙了；這只能讓她遲疑一會。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在嘗試從 Lily 手中逃走時，您需要找到並啟動分散在豪華公寓各處的三個不同的屁眼塞。它們只能在 Lily 毫無戒心的情況下從後方使用，因此需要您運用策略和創意。</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/e7b68ab536231241a5a75dcec4d2ddd8.poster.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/e7b68ab536231241a5a75dcec4d2ddd8.webm?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/e7b68ab536231241a5a75dcec4d2ddd8.mp4?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，Lily 會看守遙控器，而遙控器是由多張鑰匙卡保護的。要進入遙控器，您必須先透過門掃瞄器逐一解鎖，才能最終控制 Lily。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您能智取她並奪回控制權，讓她知道誰才是真正的主宰者，還是您會屈服於她的支配地位？莉莉的挑逗和奚落會讓您提心吊膽，不敢輕舉妄動，但她總是在您身後，一舉一動都在靠近您。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊戲特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/54da9dbc964a6f06efa0e43151e7fd85.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/ee1de7e3ac61ab2dba8216c98310a320.poster.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/ee1de7e3ac61ab2dba8216c98310a320.webm?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/ee1de7e3ac61ab2dba8216c98310a320.mp4?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><u>可收集的裝備 + 自訂</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成更多的遊戲，您就能解鎖更多美味的裝扮，滿足您的慾望。乳膠、皮革、絲襪 - 您都可以選擇；一個接一個的性感造型。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不過，Lily's Labyrinth of Lust 並未止步於此，這款遊戲是為您量身打造的。改變 Lily 外貌的各個面向，讓您體驗最親密的個人體驗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/6da23ac22dfe85bcb4257d29285915de.poster.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/6da23ac22dfe85bcb4257d29285915de.webm?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/6da23ac22dfe85bcb4257d29285915de.mp4?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想讓她穿著兔女郎服在床上交配、想讓她穿著蕾絲內衣伏在辦公室的毛絨辦公桌上、想讓她在廚房裡扮演您的性感女僕？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任君選擇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但前提是您必須勝過她。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>視覺與引擎</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/823aeb6d8b4ffff2dc04313cd3934d28.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=200 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/02f0e99a66dc0d592ae996808a8d1afd.poster.avif?t=1742849812\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/02f0e99a66dc0d592ae996808a8d1afd.webm?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/02f0e99a66dc0d592ae996808a8d1afd.mp4?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lily's Labyrinth of Lust* 採用 Unreal Engine 技術，提供令人垂涎三尺、瞠目結舌的物理效果，讓世界和 Lily 的身體栩栩如生。從每個撩人的動作到動態的互動，引擎都能確保真正身歷其境的體驗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以觀察 Lily 外型的細節，從她的曲線到她的衣著，都會隨著她的動作而流暢地反應，增添追逐時的性感與強烈感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每個環境都經過精心打造，提供視覺刺激且引人入勝的遊戲體驗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/0520d923bee30486332307513f22c8df.avif?t=1742849812\" width=400 height=523 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wishlist now, my darling, and I promise I will be gentle with you! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>- Lily</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/bb616306487ed393f57c23480d0afd49.poster.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/bb616306487ed393f57c23480d0afd49.webm?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/bb616306487ed393f57c23480d0afd49.mp4?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/f5e10d48e98d863810aee5765bbdaa5d.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >親愛的，你在愜意的頂樓公寓裡的生活即將發生轉變。我會追捕你，監視你的一舉一動，而我的腦海裡只有一件事......支配。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lily's Labyrinth of Lust 是一場令人心跳加速的貓鼠遊戲。如果你能勝過我，或許你就能掌控一切，但如果被我逮到？好吧，這麼說吧，你會發現你到底能承受多少。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能承受我無情的注視，想辦法讓我分心，抵抗我的嘲弄，努力跟上我的步伐嗎？還是你會投降，讓我帶你經歷一場永生難忘的狂野旅程？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>- 莉莉(Lily)</i></p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/773523458ac125752f9ba40fb8458c0f.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/b1996e8b9c0722aeea68a9a39ca1d23d.poster.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/b1996e8b9c0722aeea68a9a39ca1d23d.webm?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/b1996e8b9c0722aeea68a9a39ca1d23d.mp4?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>角色/「誰是莉莉？」</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lily 是你的女朋友，但別被她的愛情騙了--她是一個被控制欲驅使的花癡。她不顧一切地追逐你，不惜一切讓你屈服。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一開始，Lily 可能看起來很俏皮、很愛挑逗，但不要被她騙了。隨著遊戲的進展，Lily 會變得更加無情，讓她變得更具侵略性，並會注意到您的一舉一動。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她俏皮的奚落語在您耳邊迴盪，讓您不敢貿然逃走，然而每一次嘗試，她都會以火熱的決心拉近距離。一旦她盯上你，你就無法逃脫她無比的飢渴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lily 不只是在追逐您，她也在玩弄您的情緒。準備好迎接她意想不到的行為轉變，不要被她的甜言蜜語所迷惑，不管她看起來有多有說服力。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/1dfdeba352b6c735eec260ff84cd4850.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=200 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/ca2123eb67efaa8bb091789d651d22d6.poster.avif?t=1742849812\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/ca2123eb67efaa8bb091789d651d22d6.webm?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/ca2123eb67efaa8bb091789d651d22d6.mp4?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊戲玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在她追捕您的過程中，您需要使用所有您能找到的物品，例如屁眼塞或您值得信賴的電擊槍，這些物品可能會暫時壓制她貪得無厭的慾望，但別被騙了；這只能讓她遲疑一會。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在嘗試從 Lily 手中逃走時，您需要找到並啟動分散在豪華公寓各處的三個不同的屁眼塞。它們只能在 Lily 毫無戒心的情況下從後方使用，因此需要您運用策略和創意。</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/e7b68ab536231241a5a75dcec4d2ddd8.poster.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/e7b68ab536231241a5a75dcec4d2ddd8.webm?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/e7b68ab536231241a5a75dcec4d2ddd8.mp4?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，Lily 會看守遙控器，而遙控器是由多張鑰匙卡保護的。要進入遙控器，您必須先透過門掃瞄器逐一解鎖，才能最終控制 Lily。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您能智取她並奪回控制權，讓她知道誰才是真正的主宰者，還是您會屈服於她的支配地位？莉莉的挑逗和奚落會讓您提心吊膽，不敢輕舉妄動，但她總是在您身後，一舉一動都在靠近您。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊戲特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/54da9dbc964a6f06efa0e43151e7fd85.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/ee1de7e3ac61ab2dba8216c98310a320.poster.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/ee1de7e3ac61ab2dba8216c98310a320.webm?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/ee1de7e3ac61ab2dba8216c98310a320.mp4?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><u>可收集的裝備 + 自訂</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成更多的遊戲，您就能解鎖更多美味的裝扮，滿足您的慾望。乳膠、皮革、絲襪 - 您都可以選擇；一個接一個的性感造型。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不過，Lily's Labyrinth of Lust 並未止步於此，這款遊戲是為您量身打造的。改變 Lily 外貌的各個面向，讓您體驗最親密的個人體驗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/6da23ac22dfe85bcb4257d29285915de.poster.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/6da23ac22dfe85bcb4257d29285915de.webm?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/6da23ac22dfe85bcb4257d29285915de.mp4?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想讓她穿著兔女郎服在床上交配、想讓她穿著蕾絲內衣伏在辦公室的毛絨辦公桌上、想讓她在廚房裡扮演您的性感女僕？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任君選擇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但前提是您必須勝過她。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>視覺與引擎</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/823aeb6d8b4ffff2dc04313cd3934d28.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=200 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/02f0e99a66dc0d592ae996808a8d1afd.poster.avif?t=1742849812\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/02f0e99a66dc0d592ae996808a8d1afd.webm?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/02f0e99a66dc0d592ae996808a8d1afd.mp4?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lily's Labyrinth of Lust* 採用 Unreal Engine 技術，提供令人垂涎三尺、瞠目結舌的物理效果，讓世界和 Lily 的身體栩栩如生。從每個撩人的動作到動態的互動，引擎都能確保真正身歷其境的體驗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以觀察 Lily 外型的細節，從她的曲線到她的衣著，都會隨著她的動作而流暢地反應，增添追逐時的性感與強烈感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每個環境都經過精心打造，提供視覺刺激且引人入勝的遊戲體驗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/0520d923bee30486332307513f22c8df.avif?t=1742849812\" width=400 height=523 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wishlist now, my darling, and I promise I will be gentle with you! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>- Lily</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "short_description": "Lily's Labyrinth of Lust 是一款 3D 貓與老鼠遊戲，玩家在為生存而戰的同時，還要沉溺於性欲高漲、腎上腺素激增的追逐戰中。找到並使用工具制服 Lily，或是準備好被她無限的性慾所支配。勝利的滋味會像她一樣甜嗎？", "supported_languages": "英文<strong>*</strong>, 日文, 韓文, 俄文, 簡體中文, 繁體中文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/header.jpg?t=1742849812", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1742849812", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1742849812", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows 8, 8.1, 10, 11 64bit<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i5-8400  / AMD Ryzen 5 2600X (3.5 GHz 4 Core) or equivalent<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce GTX 3050 (req. 6GB VRAM) / AMD Radeon RX 580 (req. 6GB VRAM) / Intel ARC A650<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 5 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows 8, 8.1, 10, 11 64bit<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel i7-8700 / AMD Ryzen 7 2700X (3.7 GHz 8 Core) or equivalent<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 16 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NVIDIA RTX 3060 (req. 8GB VRAM) / AMD Radeon RX 6700 XT (req. 8GB VRAM) / Intel ARC A770<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 10 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "developers": ["Erommersion Studios"], "publishers": ["Erommersion Studios"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 18800, "final": 18800, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 188"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 61, "description": "可用 HDR"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "25", "description": "冒險"}, {"id": "4", "description": "休閒"}, {"id": "23", "description": "獨立製作"}, {"id": "70", "description": "搶先體驗"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2024 年 12 月 5 日"}}}}, "us": {"2866440": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Lily’s Labyrinth of Lust", "steam_appid": 2866440, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/2d60ecdb386f16500e2389acfb531012.avif?t=1742849812\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras_big/2d60ecdb386f16500e2389acfb531012.avif?t=1742849812 width=800 height=308 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/bb616306487ed393f57c23480d0afd49.poster.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/bb616306487ed393f57c23480d0afd49.webm?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/bb616306487ed393f57c23480d0afd49.mp4?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/f5e10d48e98d863810aee5765bbdaa5d.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=200 /></span>Life in your cushy penthouse is about to take a twisted turn, my dear. I'll be hunting you down, stalking every move you make, and I've got only one thing on my mind… domination. <br> <br><i><strong>Lily's Labyrinth of Lust</strong></i> is a pulse-pounding game of cat and mouse. If you can outsmart me, maybe you'll be in control, but if I catch you? Well... let's say you'll find out exactly how much you can take. <br> <br>Can you handle my relentless gaze, find ways to keep me distracted, resist my taunts, and try to keep up? Or will you surrender and let me take you on a wild ride you'll never forget? <u> </u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>— Lily</i></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/773523458ac125752f9ba40fb8458c0f.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=200 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/b1996e8b9c0722aeea68a9a39ca1d23d.poster.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/b1996e8b9c0722aeea68a9a39ca1d23d.webm?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/b1996e8b9c0722aeea68a9a39ca1d23d.mp4?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Lily is your girlfriend, but don't let her love fool you—she's a nymphomaniac driven by an overwhelming need for control. Relentlessly chasing you down, she'll stop at nothing to pin you into submission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At first, Lily might seem playful and teasing, but don't be deceived. As the game progresses, Lily will become more relentless, aggressive, and aware of your every move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Her playful taunts echo in your ear, daring you to escape, yet she closes the distance with fiery determination with every attempt. There's no escaping her insatiable hunger once she's set her sights on you.<br><br>Lily isn't just chasing you; she's toying with your emotions too. Be ready for unexpected shifts in her behavior, and don't fall for her sweet words—no matter how convincing she may seem.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/1dfdeba352b6c735eec260ff84cd4850.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/ca2123eb67efaa8bb091789d651d22d6.poster.avif?t=1742849812\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/ca2123eb67efaa8bb091789d651d22d6.webm?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/ca2123eb67efaa8bb091789d651d22d6.mp4?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As she hunts you down, you'll need to use every item that you can find—like butt plugs or your trusty taser gun—that might momentarily suppress her insatiable desire, but don't be fooled; it only holds her back for a while.<br><br>While trying to escape from Lily, you'll need to locate and activate three separate Butt Plugs scattered throughout your luxury apartment. These can only be used when Lily is unsuspecting and from behind, requiring you to be strategic and creative.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/e7b68ab536231241a5a75dcec4d2ddd8.poster.avif?t=1742849812\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/e7b68ab536231241a5a75dcec4d2ddd8.webm?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866440/extras/e7b68ab536231241a5a75dcec4d2ddd8.mp4?t=1742849812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also, Lily guards the butt plug remote, which is secured with multiple keycards. To gain access, you'll need to unlock each one through door scanners before you can finally bring Lily under your control.  <br><br>Can you outwit her and regain control, showing her who's in charge, or will you succumb to her dominance? Lily's teasing and taunts will keep you on edge, daring you to run, but s